{"tid":739441,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"中大伏！M記SHAKE SHAKE薯條和風紫菜味係過期貨！","createTime":"2018-07-12T06:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T16:02:16.000Z","uid":163734,"like":18,"dislike":510,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"eda1036fd5ae16b71233e9a0b6b30eda23058705","tid":739441,"uid":163734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"身為SHAKE SHAKE 薯條FANS，佢一出就當然唔帶飯都要去買包來SHAKE啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢老味！一打開包粉，倒極都倒唔出都知出事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n終於「擠」晒包粉出來，你冇睇錯啊，係用「擠」呢個動詞啊，因為根本倒唔出！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位兄台埋來研究一下，呢一舊好似發咗霉，喺廚房抽油煙機括出來嘅頹固污漬，「Shake Shake粉」，邊一忽係粉啊？！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/140835_6c87d4738dd164ad1781e44dd5a72bdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F140835_6c87d4738dd164ad1781e44dd5a72bdc.jpg&h=1b25fd12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦好啦，我當佢潮濕得滯，加予外力去捽散佢，睇下會唔會好SHAKE 啲啦！佢老味！捽唔晒不特止，仲可以好似泥膠咁搓圓㩒扁，撕開任玩，真係好過癮！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n撕碎少少丟返入去SHAKE，睇下可唔可以SHAKE 晒舊野啦！佢老味，我跳埋老母麵個藍毛毛舞都SHAKE唔散啲頹固污漬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後決定放棄，拎個包裝睇下係唔係過期野。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/140819_5003561d32e1f5689d1230f6087d15ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F140819_5003561d32e1f5689d1230f6087d15ae.jpg&h=fdc3b5a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔睇尤自何，一睇把幾火！過期日期係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2018.07.26<br />\n2018.07.26<br />\n2018.07.26<br />\n2018.07.26<br />\n2018.07.26<br />\n2018.07.26<br />\n<br />\n仲有兩個禮拜到期！咁即係上年賣剩嘅貨啦！即係咁，平時食神奇食物都無所謂，過期日程都只不過係少事，呢個仲未過期都算係恩賜！之但係，你唔係畀舊油煙機頹固污漬我SHAKE LOR！！！！！！！！！堅嬲！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80c488f3c1e8d6b04f240342f130bf4c21be0b1","tid":739441,"uid":907,"like":55,"dislike":5,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:13:12.000Z","msg":"仲食M記<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eebf67bf50464c36c92415ada2eb09eda9f5021","tid":739441,"uid":43130,"like":199,"dislike":1,"score":198,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:13:35.000Z","msg":"唔係上年，係幾個月前嗰次啲賣剩蔗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c081687b50611983344b9c24327b78fe17486bab","tid":739441,"uid":9387,"like":626,"dislike":4,"score":622,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:17:28.000Z","msg":"7月26號點過期呀<br />\n你未來人?"},{"pid":"55eed5f731a73b77f44